  m_Name: 3_UnfinishSoung
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Game.Collectable.CollectableItem
  id: 3_UnfinishSoung
  headerName: 'THE UNFINISHED SONG '
  content: "(A journal entry on a nightstand)\r\n\r\nJune 14th.\r\nThe radio is nothing
    but static now, so I\u2019ve been practicing the banjo more. But the acoustics
    feel... different lately. I was playing on the porch and I stopped to tune the
    G-string, and I swear I heard the echo carry on for a full ten seconds. It didn\u2019t
    sound like my note, though. It sounded like the trees vibrating.\r\n\r\nSarah
    says it\u2019s just the wind through the Tall Pines, but the wind doesn't keep
    a melody. It\u2019s probably just the altitude playing tricks on my ears. Still,
    the hawks didn't come out today. They\u2019re staying low in the branches."
  type: 0
  icon: {fileID: 0}
  dialogData: {fileID: 0}
